summary: Comprehensive testing of Right Doers World AI-native workforce matching platform completed. Backend APIs are fully functional with 100% success rate. Frontend authentication flow and protected routes working correctly with proper security redirects.

integration_issues.issue: Direct access to /jobs, /aimee, /dashboard redirects to auth page
integration_issues.note: This is correct security behavior - not a bug

Phone OTP Send - Demo OTP returned
User Creation (Doer, Employer, Admin) - All roles created successfully
User Retrieval by ID and Phone - Working
Jobs with Filters - Division and level filtering working
Job Creation - New jobs can be posted
AIMEE AI Chat - Gemini 3 Flash integration working
Landing Page Load - Hero section, QR code, CTAs present
Authentication Page - Role selection, phone input working
OTP Flow - Send and verify OTP working
Onboarding Page - Division selection and pincode entry
Protected Routes Security - Proper authentication redirects
